                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "<style>a{color:#212121}p,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,ul,ol{margin-bottom:12px}</style><p>Add the Android notification shade to your iOS device! Nougat is integrated into your device in a seemless fashion and behaves as one would expect its equivalent in the Control Center would.</p><p>Nougat features 4 modules to provide information or manage your device with a quick swipe:</p><ul>\n<li>Time, carrier and battery status bar</li>\n<li>Brightness slider</li>\n<li>Quick settings</li>\n<li>Date and shortcuts bar</li>\n</ul><p>Nougat comes with 3 built in theme presets so you can tailor it to your desire:</p><ul>\n<li>Color scheme as would appear on a Nexus device</li>\n<li>Color scheme as would appear on a Pixel device</li>\n<li>Light theme introduced in Android Oreo</li>\n</ul><p>Configure Nougat from Settings panel, with no respring required!</p>",
